      • countValue

        public Complex_Number countValue(Complex_Number z)
        Counts value of the polynomial for complex-number z. This is done by counting values of each term of the polynomial and adding these values together.
        Parameters:
        z - Complex-number presenting point on the complex-plane (z is used to count value of the polynomial).
        Returns:
        Value of polynomial.

      • toString

        public java.lang.String toString()
